                                      .

     Community and Government Relations


       Duties: CGR conducts public meetings, media relations, handles
            intergovernmental agreements and legislative issues.

        Construction and Operations


                         Duties: roadway maintenance

                Engineering

                      Duties: roadway design

      Infrastructure Technology Center

        Duties: maintains and supports the MCDOT computer network and
        helpdesk, develops web-based applications, produces maps

                  Planning

     Duties: The Transportation Planning Division (TPD) exists to provide
     long range strategic guidance for Maricopa County transportation
     investments.

           Professional Services

                      Duties: customer service

                Right of Way

                 Duties: management of land use, acquisition


